cu.explanation_en: Setting MCC to a negative value will cause PLMN configuration validation error as MCC must be positive.

du.explanation_en: Setting physCellId to a negative value will cause invalid cell configuration as physCellId must be non-negative.
du.explanation_zh: 將 physCellId 設定為負值會導致無效的細胞配置，因為 physCellId 必須為非負數。
